textBeforeTable: Rushing (by yards) I know we’re in the heart of basketball season now, but I promised I would get these final East Bay football leaders up on the blog so here they are. Some stats you may have seen listed in bios of our All-East Bay football selections do include the playoffs, so I want to clarify that so there’s no confusion.
